sequenceDiagram
  participant BR as Browser (React)
  participant BG as Bridge (Flask-SocketIO)
  participant GS as GameServer (Pyro5)

  BR->>BG: socket.emit('submit_hint', {hint_word})
  BG->>GS: proxy.submit_hint(player_id, hint_word) via Pyro5 RPC
  GS->>BG: @oneway on_hint_received(data) para todos callbacks
  BG->>BR: socketio.emit('hint_received', data, to=room_code)
